Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:15.15,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}点着头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:17.98,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}「总会有办法的啊」把问题全部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:19.39,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.15}{\pos(352,510)}{\fad(0,500)}抛于脑后
